headline: M&T Bank Corporation Announces Third Quarter 2025 Earnings Release and Conference Call
summary: M&T Bank Corporation ("M&T") (NYSE:MTB) plans to announce its third quarter 2025 earnings results in a press release that will be issued before the market opens on Thursday, October 16, 2025.

headline: M&T Bank Decreases Prime Rate
summary: Effective Thursday, September 18, 2025, M&T Bank Corporation ("M&T") (NYSE:MTB) will decrease its prime lending rate from 7.50% to 7.25%.
